        <property name="toolTip">
         <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Attach an Arnold &lt;b&gt;aiStandardSurface&lt;/b&gt; bridge to each material in scope. The material's textures are mirrored onto the Arnold shader, wired to the shading group's &lt;b&gt;aiSurfaceShader&lt;/b&gt; slot — so the asset renders in Arnold while the exported Stingray / Standard Surface material is untouched. Skips materials that already have a bridge (unless &lt;b&gt;Force&lt;/b&gt; is on).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
        </property>
